include ../mixins/container

- var values = { title: 'Order Conditional Companion', name: 'OrderConditionalCompanion', class: 'order-conditional-companion', page: 'page X', radio: 'order_conditional_companion', stat: ``, stat_repeat: '', roll: true }
+container(values)
  p When <strong>you ask a conditional companion to act for something not akin to their drives, motivations or the fulfillment of their goal</strong>, or if the conditional companion is a hireling, roll +loyalty. If you share a bond, you may reroll any dice.
  p On a <strong>strong hit</strong>, your Conditional Companion Acts, but suffer -1 to their loyalty.
  p On a <strong>weak hit</strong>, your Conditional Companion Acts, but not without whimper. Suffer -2 to their loyalty.
  p On a <strong>miss</strong>, your conditional companion refuses to follow your request. Suffer -2 to their loyalty.